trans-unit.source: Provides a dialog box for editing regular expressions used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RegularExpressionValidator"></xref>.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RegexEditorDialog"></xref> class.
The site for this dialog box.
Represents the method that will handle the Help event of the dialog box.
The source of the event.
An <xref href="System.EventArgs"></xref> object that provides data for the event.
Represents the method that will handle the OK event of the dialog box.
The source of the event.
An <xref href="System.EventArgs"></xref> object that provides data for the event.
Represents the method that will handle the **TestValidate** event of the dialog box.
The source of the event.
An <xref href="System.EventArgs"></xref> object that provides data for the event.
Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RegexEditorDialog"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
This method is called by the public <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component.Dispose%2A> method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
<xref:System.ComponentModel.Component.Dispose%2A> invokes the protected <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RegexEditorDialog.Dispose%2A> method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
<xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
When the `disposing` parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RegexEditorDialog> references.
This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
A value indicating to all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RegexEditorDialog"></xref> references.
Represents the method that will handle the SelectedIndexChanged event of the dialog box.
The source of the event.
An <xref href="System.EventArgs"></xref> object that provides data for the event.
Represents the method that will handle the Activated event of dialog box.
The source of the event.
An <xref href="System.EventArgs"></xref> object that provides data for the event.
Gets or sets the name of the regular expression to edit.
The name of the regular expression.
Represents the method that will handle the **TextChanged** event of the dialog box.
The source of the event.
An <xref href="System.EventArgs"></xref> object that provides data for the event.
